divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting on my front porch smoking a cig when i saw something out the corner of my eye to the right. I looked up in the sky and saw a sphere pulsating and move very slow in the sky. It looked very high in the sky traveling south to north! I lost it once it moved behind some trees. I took some pictures with a ViviCam3785, zoom in on the pictures and you can see the sphere.
